   "body" : "Revives #18242. Depends on #20962 (please review that first, the first two commits are from there).\r\n\r\nLatest BIP324 draft is [here](https://gist.github.com/dhruv/5b1275751bc98f3b64bcafce7876b489) (not submitted to the BIP repository since it's still under work; the changes being made do not affect this PR).\r\n\r\nThis PR adds a p2p message transport {de}serializer for encrypted message after BIP324. The code is exclusively used in the tests.\r\n\r\nIncludes:\r\n* AEAD handling\r\n* short command IDs\r\n* unit and fuzz tests\r\n\r\nExcludes (to keep it reviewable):\r\n* The handshake\r\n* ECDH (enabling libsecp256k1 & CKey implementation)\r\n* Service flag (to signal v2 support) and a way to globally enable it",
